How to run the program:


Press run application or compile and execute the program.
After successfully stated the application open any browser and navigate to 127.0.0.1:8080

There are 2 endpoints for this application:
127.0.0.1:8080/rates
127.0.0.1:8080/conversion

Rates: Returns all exchange rates for a specific currency. base= defines the base currency. Example: 127.0.0.1:8080/rates?base=USD
returns all exchange rates for USD.

Conversion: Returns a list of specified exchange rates and can also convert an amount to those currencies.
Examples:

127.0.0.1:8080/conversion?base=USD&symbols=EUR,CNY,BYN,GBP
returns the exchange rate of USD to EUR, CNY, BYN, GBP
127.0.0.1:8080/conversion?base=USD&symbols=EUR,CNY,BYN,GBP&amount500
returns the conversion of 500 USD to EUR, CNY, BYN, GBP

In case you would like to change the port please do so in application.properties

Also SWAGGER available at: 127.0.0.1:8080/swagger-ui/index.html
